title: #36 - How to Sneak into a Drake Video & Reacting to Ricegum's Return
itunes:title: #36 - How Tim Chantarangsu Snuck into a Drake Music Video
description: On this in-studio episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, rapper, comedian, content creator Tim Chantarangsu comes on the show to talk about how he snuck onto a Drake and Justin Bieber music video, dropping his Timothy DeLaGhetto stage name, why he'd love to be in the next Back to the Future, Ricegum's return to YouTube, and more!
